TO PERSONALIZE: EMAIL ME AFTER PURCHASE WITH DETAILS This XXLG functional duffle style diaper bag or tote bag is made with a creme fabric and has western items all over it. Great for your cell phone, kindle, newspaper, diapers, water bottle etc. Choice for closure: zipper closure, magnetic snap, button and loop, Velcro, ribbon or a cloth tie or I have a wide top brown swirl fabric zipper top. The dimensions are : 21" across the top, 15" high and 6 x 14" wide bottom. The extra wide comfortable handles are 31" long.
